9. SECURITY IMPLEMENTATION

The platform incorporates several security mechanisms:

Password hashing using Werkzeug Security.
Session timeout management.
AWS IAM access controls.
Security Group configuration.
Restricted database access.
File type validation during uploads.

These measures help ensure data confidentiality and application security.

10. RESULTS

The project successfully achieved its objectives by integrating AWS cloud services with a Flask-based web application.

Key achievements include:

Successful deployment on AWS EC2.
Secure user authentication system.
Cloud-based storage using Amazon S3.
Managed database implementation using Amazon RDS.
Responsive web interface.
Reliable content delivery mechanism.

The platform demonstrates practical cloud computing concepts and serves as a foundation for future educational technologies.

