12. CONCLUSION

The AWS-Hosted Virtual Classroom and Learning Platform successfully demonstrates the integration of modern cloud computing services with web application technologies. By leveraging Amazon EC2, Amazon RDS, and Amazon S3, the platform provides a secure, scalable, and efficient educational environment.

The project highlights key cloud computing principles, including infrastructure deployment, cloud storage, database management, and application hosting. It serves as an excellent example of a cloud-native educational solution and provides a strong foundation for future expansion into enterprise-scale learning systems.

